{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GeolocationPosition","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">Geolocation API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>GeolocationPosition</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition/coords\"><code>coords</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geolocation API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>GeolocationCoordinates</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPositionError\"><code>GeolocationPositionError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>Navigator.geolocation</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">secure contexts (en-US)</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>GeolocationPosition</code></strong> 인터페이스는 주어진 시간에 장치가 위치한 지점을 나타냅니다</span>. 지점은 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>Coordinates</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 객체로 표현하여, 지구를 나타내는 회전타원체 위의 2D 위치와 더불어 높이와 속도 정보를 담습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"속성","title":"속성","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>GeolocationPosition</code> 인터페이스는 어떤 속성도 상속하지 않습니다.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"position.coords_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition/coords\"><code>Position.coords</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>주어진 시간의 위치를 나타내는 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationCoordinates\"><code>Coordinates</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 객체입니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"position.timestamp_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition/timestamp\"><code>Position.timestamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"This feature is available only in secure contexts (HTTPS)\">Secure context</span></dt>\n <dd>위치를 기록한 시간을 나타내는 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>입니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"메서드","title":"메서드","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>GeolocationPosition</code> 인터페이스는 어떤 메서드도 상속하거나 구현하지 않습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#position\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Geolocation API<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'Position' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"api.GeolocationPosition","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"같이_보기","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">위치정보 사용하기</a></li>\n <li>이 인터페이스를 사용하는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a> 인터페이스.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"속성","id":"속성"},{"text":"메서드","id":"메서드"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"같이_보기"}],"summary":"GeolocationPosition 인터페이스는 주어진 시간에 장치가 위치한 지점을 나타냅니다","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GeolocationPosition","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Position","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"GeolocationPosition","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GeolocationPosition","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Position","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GeolocationPosition","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Position","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Posi